{"tid":469870,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"恆生管理學院校長：國歌法正式立法後　或會修訂校規","createTime":"2017-11-15T18:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T01:08:24.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08ff813c140c6a10599c58f73e5b4ed6a0ef3097","tid":469870,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"恆生管理學院今早舉行畢業禮，校長何順文在畢業禮後回應有關國歌法本地立法的問題時，表示若國歌法正式在本地立法，「如果按規章，可能亦會看規章是否需要作一些修訂」。<br />\n<br />\n何順文在畢業禮上致辭時，表示期望學生可以實現自己的志趣及價值觀，不應隨便跟隨權威或主流的期望；他認為大學應培養人文素養多於學習技能或找工作。<br />\n<br />\n身兼河南省政協委員的何順文指，學校不會在畢業禮播放國歌。被問若國歌法在本地立法後，學校會否有任何措施配合，何表示，現時政府仍在進行相關前期工作，學校管理層尚未有任何討論，但會留意事態發展，一旦立法<span style=\"color: red;\">，會考慮校規是否需要作修訂。他指學校原有規例已說明學生不應在學校作出不當行為，又強調若有學生在播放國歌期間，態度欠缺嚴肅，「當然要先教育他們」。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171115/s00001/1510738997979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171115%2Fs00001%2F1510738997979&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5a54093e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171115%2Fs00001%2F1510738997979&h=9789db6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171115/s00001/1510738997979</a>"},{"pid":"a79f59501712643f86e5e9940f40db1c22af15e9","tid":469870,"uid":130543,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:07:01.000Z","msg":"恆大領先八大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全港第一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPound of my school!!!"},{"pid":"8f6f2c6728a92124a9aa22aa48a218bde41b7a41",